─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
THIRD-PARTY DATA ATTRIBUTION
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

The processed dataset is derived from the following publicly
available sources. Users must comply with the terms of each
upstream source when redistributing derived data:

World Bank World Development Indicators (WDI)
  Provider  : The World Bank
  Licence   : Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 (CC BY 4.0)
  URL       : https://data.worldbank.org/
  Terms     : https://www.worldbank.org/en/about/legal/terms-of-use-for-datasets

World Bank Worldwide Governance Indicators (WGI)
  Provider  : The World Bank / Kaufmann, Kraay & Mastruzzi
  Licence   : Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 (CC BY 4.0)
  URL       : https://info.worldbank.org/governance/wgi/
  Citation  : Kaufmann D., Kraay A. and Mastruzzi M. (2010).
              "The Worldwide Governance Indicators: A Summary
              of Methodology, Data and Analytical Issues."
              World Bank Policy Research Working Paper No. 5430.

UNESCO Institute for Statistics (UIS)
  Provider  : UNESCO Institute for Statistics
  Licence   : Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 IGO
              (CC BY-SA 3.0 IGO)
  URL       : https://uis.unesco.org/
  Terms     : https://uis.unesco.org/en/terms-and-conditions
  Note      : Users of derived data must attribute UNESCO UIS
              and indicate whether changes were made. Derived
              works must be shared under the same or compatible
              licence terms.
